      "title": "Middleware Execution Order Rules",
      "headers": ["Rule", "Description", "Example"],
      "rows": [
        ["Order matters", "Middleware runs in the order defined", "Define logging before routes"],
        ["next() required", "Must call next() to continue chain", "Omitting next() causes request to hang"],
        ["Error middleware last", "Error handlers must come after all routes", "app.use((err, req, res, next) => {})"],
